'''2016年8月緬甸地震'''是2016年8月24日在[[緬甸|緬甸]]當地時間17時34分（UTC+6:30）發生的[[黎克特制|黎克特制]]6.8級地震，震央位於緬甸中北部、[[伊洛瓦底江|伊洛瓦底江]]沿岸城鎮[[稍埠鎮|稍埠]]（Chauk）以西{{convert|25|km|mi|abbr=on}}處<ref name='rfi'/><ref name='mmt'>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mmtimes.com/index.php/national-news/22126-powerful-6-8-magnitude-earthquake-hits-central-myanmar.html|title=Powerful earthquake hits central Myanmar|agency=[[法新社|AFP]]/緬甸時報|location=|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824141323/http://www.mmtimes.com/index.php/national-news/22126-powerful-6-8-magnitude-earthquake-hits-central-myanmar.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，距離熱門旅遊景點古都[[蒲甘|蒲甘]]約{{convert|25|mi|km|abbr=on|order=flip}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/24/myanmar-struck-by-6-8-magnitude-earthquake|title=Myanmar struck by 6.8-magnitude earthquake|agency=衛報|location=曼谷|first=Oliver|last=Holmes|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en-gb|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824143831/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/24/myanmar-struck-by-6-8-magnitude-earthquake|dead-url=no}}</ref>。震源估計深度為{{convert|84.1|km|mi|abbr=on}}<ref name=USGS/>，[[麥加利地震烈度|最高烈度]]為6度（強烈），此次地震在緬甸多處亦能感受搖晃，更甚鄰國[[孟加拉|孟加拉]][[達卡|達卡]]、[[泰國|泰國]][[曼谷|曼谷]]及[[印度|印度]][[加爾各答|加爾各答]]均可感到震動。<ref name='rfi'>{{Cite news|url=http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=290901|title=緬甸中北部規模6.8強震 未傳傷亡|agency=[[中央廣播電台|央廣]]|location=台北|author=黃啟霖|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=zh-tw|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826120312/http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=290901|archivedate=2016-08-26|df=}}</ref><ref name='bbc'>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37172794|title=Myanmar earthquake: One dead and temples damaged|agency=[[BBC|BBC]]|location=|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en-gb|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824180144/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-37172794|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/earthquake-of-6-8/3070270.html|title=Powerful earthquakes strikes central Myanmar, rattles region|agency=[[亞洲新聞頻道|亞洲新聞頻道]]|location=新加坡|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824113521/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/earthquake-of-6-8/3070270.html|archivedate=2016-08-24}}</ref><ref name='bp'/>

地震在緬甸至少造成3人死亡<ref name='mmt'/><ref name='bbc'/><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-quake-idUSKCN10Z176?il=0|title=Powerful earthquake strikes central Myanmar, at least three dead|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|location=仰光|author1=Shwe Yee Saw Myint|author2=Aung Hla Tun|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160826130830/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-quake-idUSKCN10Z176?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>，古都蒲甘則有多座古廟宇損毀<ref name='mmt'/><ref name='bbc'/><ref name='bp'>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/1069977/bangkok-high-rises-shaken-by-myanmar-earthquake|title=Bangkok high rises shaken by Myanmar earthquake|agency=曼谷郵報|location=曼谷|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en}}</ref><ref name='cna'>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201608245024-1.aspx|title=緬甸中部6.8地震 已知1死60座佛塔毀損|agency=中央社|location=台北|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=zh-tw|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825183047/http://www2.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201608245024-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而加爾各答的地下鐵服務一度因此需要暫停<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ndtv.com/kolkata-news/kolkata-metro-services-halted-briefly-after-fresh-tremors-758252|title=Kolkata Metro Services Halted Briefly After Fresh Tremors|agency=NDTV|location=加爾各答|author=|date=2016-08-24|accessdate=2016-08-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828020929/http://www.ndtv.com/kolkata-news/kolkata-metro-services-halted-briefly-after-fresh-tremors-758252|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

